   <taskbody>
      <context class="- topic/section task/context ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">During multiple rounds of negotiation, the text of a clause in your agreement is likely to be modified. </p>
         <p class="- topic/p ">Changes to clauses can be tracked over multiple check-ins, as long as redlining is preserved. Changes to clauses only become permanent when the document is checked in and <xref href="../reconciliation_45220099_45220099/45220099.dita"
                  format="dita"
                  class="- topic/xref ">reconciled</xref>.  </p>
         <p class="- topic/p ">To reject the changes to a clause:</p>
      </context>
      <steps class="- topic/ol task/steps ">
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Hover over the <image placement="inline"
                      width="20"
                      href="../attachments/45220112/49086827.png"
                      id="image_zxd_pv4_12c"
                      class="- topic/image "/>
               <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Document </b>tab and select <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Clauses</b> to open the Documents Panel.</cmd>
            <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">
               <fig class="- topic/fig ">
                  <image height="250"
                         placement="break"
                         width="262"
                         href="../attachments/45220112/51576893.png"
                         class="- topic/image "/>
               </fig>
            </info>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Click on <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Show Only Changed Clauses</uicontrol> to display a list of
               clauses with changes since the last check-in.</cmd>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Right-click on the changed clause in the Document pane (highlighted in red) and
               select <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Reject Changes</uicontrol>. </cmd>
         </step>
      </steps>
      <result id="result_c2h_sv4_12c" class="- topic/section task/result ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">The clause is reverted to its previous value prior to the change. The Document pane
            reloads to show the change.</p>
      </result>
